name: black - CONTACT SELLER FOR ORDER DETAILS
description:
The hood.e is made of a soft fleece. It does not require batteries, but runs off the power of your mp3.  It is also available in Black, Navy, White, Blue, Maroon, Forest Green, Red, Heather Grey, Yellow, Dark Grey, Purple and Speckled Grey.

Hood.e is not in mass production. All orders are custom made at this stage which means high attention to detail.

Custom embroidery is available at an additional cost. Please email for more information.

Dry clean only.

Please allow 2-3 weeks for delivery.
